messages.content: I was hoping you would actually stand up in the interview with me

Certainly! Standing up during an interview can indeed make a positive impression and show a sense of confidence and engagement. It can also help you project your voice better and appear more energetic. In your experience, have you found that standing up during interviews has had a noticeable impact on the dynamics or outcomes of the conversation?

transcript:
Participant: I was hoping you would actually stand up in the interview with me

Moderator: Certainly! Standing up during an interview can indeed make a positive impression and show a sense of confidence and engagement. It can also help you project your voice better and appear more energetic. In your experience, have you found that standing up during interviews has had a noticeable impact on the dynamics or outcomes of the conversation?
